{"id": "rios022", "name": "Cam_TsukiSt_497_04_04", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n...... Rin...\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "So still...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I... hurt humans. The Administration Bureau should have sent an Architect to recycle me long ago...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Outside... I don't see a single human... What on earth happened...?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I always knew that my existence would sooner or later cause problems...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "You said... You lost people you cared for, so you wanted to end your life. At the time... I couldn't understand what you meant...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "But I... I thought many times, if I were obliterated, would it be... But, I'm scared, so scared... I tried with all my might to not let this happen again, and yet the result was...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I don't have any idea what I am... to the Architects, I'm just a malfunctioning defect; to humans I'm not even close to a qualified Architect; and to the Blessed...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "All this... You can't even hear me anymore, can you...?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Is this... death? It looks exactly like you're sleeping... Perhaps death is not as scary as I imagined...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Humans believe that you go to another world when you die. I... Can I see you in that world...?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\nCan't stay here... a grave. After dying, humans are put in a grave. Is that how they get to the other world? It must be!\n\n\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "Stands up"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Shovel", "Digging"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "This should do it? Rin...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I don't know... if when an Architect is shut down that means they are dead, and I don't know if Architect's death and human's are the same...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "If I want to go to another world, I must have to go in a grave... an Architect's grave...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Is that... an Architect...?</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen B"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">They haven't disappeared! Is she digging a grave...?\nHey! Over here!</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "Sprints"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "She... She ran away...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen B"], "content": "The alert may have ended, but we still must stay on guard. Don't know where those things disappeared to...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "Wreaking havoc all of a sudden, then they all disappear. Now, everything's stopped working...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen B"], "content": "Is this the end of the world...?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "... What are you talking about? We're still alive... We'll get through this, even if we don't have any Architects.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "Sprints"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Can't... Can't see.\nBut my positioning system and sonar are still operational. I just need to get there...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Shelter 03... The place where I was made. Also the place I ought to be returned to when I'm destroyed.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\nHow could... What a huge number of Architect tags... Did everybody... come here? They all... were destroyed... Could it have been...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Those people said... all the Architects disappeared...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "It must... be here. The Architect's grave...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Sits Down"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin... Soon... I'll see you...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "System shuts down"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n……凛……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "静か……だね……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "私……人間を傷つけた……\n管理局は……どうしてもっと早く他のアーキテクトに私を回収させなかったの……？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "なのに……外には誰もいない……\nなにが、あったの……？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "私の存在が……いつか問題を引き起こすってわかってたのに……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛……あなたは、大切な人を失ってしまったから、自分の命も終わりにしようって思ったって言ってたよね……\nなにを言ってるのかわからなかった……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "でもね……いっそ私もこのまま消えることができたらなんて……何度も考えた……\nでも、怖くて。\n怖くて……何も起こらないように頑張ってみたけど……結果は……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "私、私が何者なのかわからない……\nアーキテクトから見れば、私はただの不良品。\nでも、人類にとっては私はアーキテクトですらない存在……\nしゅくふく……されし者……か。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "もう……あなたには何も聞こえてないのかな……？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "これが……死……？\n眠ってるようにしか見えないのに……\n「死」って、私が思うほど恐ろしいものじゃないのかな……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "人類は……死んだらもうひとつの世界に行くって信じてるんだよね。\nなら……私は？\nその世界で、またあなたと会える……？凛。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\nなら、このままここにいるわけにはいかないね……\nお墓……人類は死んじゃったらお墓に入るんだよね。\nそれが、新しい世界へ行くための方法？うん、きっとそう！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "立ち上がる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Shovel", "土を掘る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "これでいいかな？\n凛……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "シャットダウンが……アーキテクトにとって「死」を意味するのかどうかは分からないけど……\nううん、そもそもアーキテクトにとっての「死」が人間と同じものなのかどうかも分からない……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "でも、私もその世界へ行くためにはお墓に入らないといけないよね……\nアーキテクトのお墓……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">あれは……！アーキテクトか……？</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">やっぱりまだ残ってたんだ！\n墓を……作っているのか……？\nおい！こっちだ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "に……逃げられたか……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "警報は解除されたが、まだ安心はできないな。\nあいつはいったいどこへ……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "急に破壊活動を始めたかと思ったら、今度は急に跡形もなく消えやがった……\nそのせいであらゆる施設がとまっちまったよ……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "これが……世界の終わり……ってやつか？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "……なに言ってんだ？\n俺たちはまだみんな生きてる……\nアーキテクトがいなくたって、なんとかなるさ。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "目が……見えない……\nでも位置情報システムとソナーはまだ使えるみたいだから……\nあそこにたどり着けさえすれば……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Shelter03……私が、作られた場所。\nそして、破棄された後に来るべき場所……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\nこれは……！\nアーキテクトのタグがこんなにたくさん……みんな……ここへ？\nみんな……破壊されてる……これはいったい……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "さっきあの人たちは……アーキテクトが消えたって言ってた……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "なら……間違いない。\nここがアーキテクトの「墓」……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "座る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛……今……会いに行くよ……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "シャットダウン"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n……凜……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "好安靜……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……傷害了人類，管理局應該早就要派其他建造者來把我回收了……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "外面……卻連一個人類也看不見……到底發生什麼事了……？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我一直都知道，我的存在遲早會造成問題……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "妳說……失去了最重要的人，所以想結束自己的生命，當下……我不能理解妳在說什麼……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不過我……我也好幾次想過，如果就這樣被銷毀，是不是……但是，我真的好害怕，害怕到用盡一切力量……試圖讓這一切不要發生，結果還是……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我根本不知道，自己到底算什麼……對建造者來說，我只是出錯的瑕疵品；對人類來說，我連個稱職的建造者都算不上；對眷顧者……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "說這些……妳也已經聽不見了吧……？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "這就是……死嗎……？妳看起來，只像是睡著了一樣……也許死亡沒有我想像中的那麼可怕……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "人類相信死後會去到另一個世界，我……也能在那個世界再見到妳嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n那就不能繼續待在這裡了……墳墓，人類死後都會被放進墳墓中，那就是你們前往那個世界的方法吧？一定是的！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "站立"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Shovel", "鏟土"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "這樣就行了吧？凜……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我不知道……建造者的關機是否就代表死亡，也不知道建造者的死亡是否跟人類一樣……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "如果我也想去另一個世界，也要進到墳墓才行吧……建造者的墳墓……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">那個……是建造者嗎……？</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">果然還沒有完全消失！她在挖墳墓……？\n喂！這邊！</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "跑……跑走了……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "雖然警報已經解除了，但還是不能放鬆戒心，那些傢伙不知道消失到哪去了……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "突然就開始大肆破壞，現在又是全部消失，所有設施也都因為這樣停擺了……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "這是世界末日嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "……你在說什麼？我們都還活著啊……我們會挺過去的，就算沒有建造者。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "看……看不見。\n不過定位系統和聲納還能運作，只要到那個地方……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Shelter 03……我被製造的地方，也是銷毀後該來的地方……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n怎麼會……這麼大量的建造者標籤……大家……都跑來這裡了？全部都……被摧毀了……到底是……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "剛剛那些人類說……所有建造者都消失了……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "那一定……就是這裡了，建造者的「墳墓」……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "坐下"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凜……我很快……去見妳……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "系統關機"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n......Rin......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "조용하다...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "나는... 인간을 해쳤으니... 관리국은 다른 아키텍트를 파견해서 날 회수하려고 하겠지....\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "바깥에... 사람이라곤 한 명도 보이지 않아... 대체 무슨 일이... 벌어졌던 거지...?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "난 줄곧 알고 있었어.... \n내 존재 자체가... 진작에... 큰 문제를 일으킬 수 있다는 것을...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "네가 말했지... 가장 소중한 사람을 잃고 나서... 죽을 생각이었다고... 그땐... 네가 왜 그런 말을 하는지 이해하지 못 했어....\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "하지만 나... 나도 몇 번이나 생각했었어... 만약 이대로 폐기되버린다면 나는.... 하지만... 나는 정말로 무서웠어... 너무 무서워서 최선을 다하려고 했어.... 이 모든 일이 발생하지 않도록.... 하지만 결과는...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "난 내가 대체 어떤 존재인지 모르겠어... 아키텍트에겐 난 그저 불량품... 인간들에겐 업무용 아키텍트 취급조차 받지 못하고...권고자들에게는...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "지금 하는 말... 이제 네게는 안 들리겠지...?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "이것이... 죽음인가...? 그냥 봐서는... 잠을 자고 있는 것만 같은데... 죽음이란 것이... 내가 생각했던 것보다 그렇게 무서운 건 아니었나봐...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "인간들은 죽음 이후에 다른 세계로 간다고 믿고 있잖아? ... 나도... 그 세계로 가면 널 다시 만날 수 있는 걸까...?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\n그럼 나도 계속 이곳에 있지 않을래...\n무덤... 그래, 인간들은 죽은 이후 무덤으로 들어가지? 분명 그것이 죽음 이후의 세계로 갈 수 있는 통로인 거지? 그렇지?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "일어선다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Shovel", "땅을 판다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "이렇게 하면 되는 거야? Rin...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아키텍트의 전원이 꺼지는 것도... 죽음에 속하는 건지... 아키텍트가 죽어도... 인간들처럼 그 세계에 갈 수 있을지... 난 잘 모르겠어.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "만약 내가 그 세계로 가고 싶다면... 무덤으로 들어가야겠지... 아키텍트들의 무덤으로...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">저건... 아키텍트...?</font>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 B"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">역시 전부 사라진 게 아니었어! 지금 무덤을 파고 있는 거야...?\n 이봐! 이쪽이야!</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "달린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "도... 도망쳤어...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 B"], "content": "경보가 이미 해제됐지만, 그래도 역시 방심해선 안 돼. 그 녀석들은 대체 어디로 가버린 거지...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "갑자기 마구잡이로 파괴하더니, 지금은 또 전부 사라져버렸어. 모든 설비들도 작동을 멈춰버렸고...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 B"], "content": "이것이... 세계 종말... 이란 건가...?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "....무슨 소리야? 우리가 살아남았잖아... 우리 인간들은 계속 나아갈 수 있을 거야... 아키텍트 없이도 말이야...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "달린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "어... 없어졌어.\n그래도 위치 시스템과 초음파 장치는 아직 작동시킬 수 있어... 그곳에 가기만 하면...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Shelter 03... 내가 제작된 곳... 그리고...폐기됐을 때 다시 돌아오게 될 곳이기도 해...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\n말도 안 돼... 어떻게... 아키텍트 라벨이 이렇게나 많이... 모두들... 이곳으로 옮겨진 건가? 전부... 페기됐어... 이건 대체...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "방금 그 인간이... 모든 아키텍트가 사라졌다고 말했었는데...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "그렇다면 분명... 이곳이... 아키텍트의... [무덤]...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "앉는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin... 금방... 만나러 갈게.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "시스템 종료"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n……凜……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "好安靜……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……傷害了人類，管理局應該早就要派其他建造者來把我回收了……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "外面……卻連一個人類也看不見……到底發生什麼事了……？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我一直都知道，我的存在遲早會造成問題……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "妳說……失去了最重要的人，所以想結束自己的生命，當下……我不能理解妳在說什麼……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conv